[{"type":"message","text":"<https://groups.google.com/d/msg/vim_jp/3DWz3rTDU5g/gtLkNrZ4AwAJ|ubuntu 上でのgvim のwindow の横幅>\nubuntu 18.04の上でgvim(ver 8.2)を使わせていただいています。 画面(Winodw)の横幅がコラム数85より小さくすることができません。 縦幅は画面一杯から1まで変更可能です。 どのようにすれば横幅を変更することができるでしょうか。","ts":"1587367341.080200","subtype":"bot_message","bot_id":"BPV6T0C1J","username":"vim_jp","icons":{"image_48":"https://a.slack-edge.com/80588/img/services/rss_48.png"},"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null},{"client_msg_id":"45c04730-8bfc-4fcd-8306-5bc1881e85b9","type":"message","user":"UJV04G927","text":"質問です。\nlightline.vimの表示なのですが、fzf.vimをpopup window(in Vim8)で使用するとlightline.vimが正常に表示されません。\n同じような事象の方などいらっしゃいましたら解決策等教えていただきたいです。\n```set laststatus=2 \ncall plug#begin(expand('$XDG_DATA_HOME/vim/plugged'))\n\" global\nPlug 'itchyny/lightline.vim'\nPlug 'junegunn/fzf'\ncall plug#end()\n\nlet g:fzf_layout = { 'window': { 'width': 0.95, 'height': 0.9 } }```\nvimrcはこれで再現します。","ts":"1587370822.082400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"qek"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"9aa90566-7ffa-4ead-970a-423c1c84a57e","type":"message","user":"UJV04G927","text":"fzfで選択したり、キャンセルして戻ってくるとこんな感じになります。","ts":"1587370859.082500","files":[{"id":"F01251JLH7V","created":1587370858,"timestamp":1587370858,"name":"スクリーンショット 2020-04-20 17.09.16.png","title":"スクリーンショット 2020-04-20 17.09.16.png","mimetype":"image/png","image_exif_rotation":0,"filetype":"png","pretty_type":"PNG","user":"UJV04G927","mode":"hosted","editable":false,"is_external":false,"external_type":"","size":9219,"url":"","url_download":"","url_private":"https://files.slack.com/files-pri/T03C4RC8V-F01251JLH7V/____________________________2020-04-20_17.09.16.png","url_private_download":"https://files.slack.com/files-pri/T03C4RC8V-F01251JLH7V/download/____________________________2020-04-20_17.09.16.png","original_h":36,"original_w":1138,"thumb_64":"htt